reviewText: Even though this video is dated, it still is a lot of fun to watch with young kids!  And, the Biblical truths that are taught in such a creative way, will stick with parents and kids for life!
My daughter always loved this video and wanted it for Christmas.  We received it in good condition. Would like find it in DVD.
I have been looking for this video for a long time. My kids simply loved it when they were toddlers. Now my grandchildren love it also.
